Overall, pretty good. I enjoy this type of sim game, but I noticed the side-view mirror does not show the actual view to the left of the truck unless the inset mirrors are activated. Somewhat disappointing. Pedals are small and hard to hit, especially when using the fully manual transmission. If the graphic remained the same size but the sensitive area was increased about twice, it would be much more fun to operate the manual transmission. Right now it is an exercise in frustration. Also, the gear shift buttons should have an option to be on the left side of the screen, next to the brake, so shifting is more fluid. Steering is a bit weird: turning the wheel or tilting your device will cause the truck to drift, even if you only make the slightest turns.
